data.description: RUN, don't walk to this amazing first time offering in one of southeast orange counties most convenient neighborhoods! Welcome to Waterford Trails! Minutes to downtown Avalon Park, Waterford Lakes Town Center, the University of Central Florida, Cocoa Beach, Orlando International Airport, Sanford-Orlando Airport and Cape Canaveral Cruise Port. Easy access as well to all of the area attractions by way of the nearby expressways! This single story home boasts 4 bedrooms (one of which could be a great in-home office) split bedroom plan, living/dining room combo, eat-in-kitchen/family room combo inside utility, 2 car garage and a fenced backyard. The community has a low HOA fee and NO CDD.  New Roof: replaced in 2022.  New Water heater: replaced in 2023.  Seller is motivated to sell fast so submit your highest and best offer TODAY!!
